headline: Agoda unveils the most 'paw-some' cities in Asia to travel with pets
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has announced its ranking of the top 10 most pet-friendly travel destinations in Asia, highlighting the growing trend of travelers seeking accommodations that welcome their furry companions. The list, calculated based on the average number of accommodations allowing pets, reveals cities in Vietnam dominate the list, securing four out of ten spots.
